    • Field Detail

      • id

        public int id
        This Swarm Achievement's unique integer identification number.

      • orderId

        public int orderId
        Identifies this Swarm Achievement's position in the Swarm Achievement list. The Swarm Achievement with an orderId of 0 will be shown first in the list.

      • title

        public java.lang.String title
        The title of this Swarm Achievement that is displayed to the user in the app's achievement list and in the Swarm Notification that is shown to the user when this achievement is unlocked.

      • description

        public java.lang.String description
        The description that tells the user how to unlock this achievement.

      • points

        public int points
        The number of Swarm Points that a user will earn by unlocking this achievement.

      • hidden

        public boolean hidden
        If true, this achievement is not visible to the user in the app's list of achievements until it is unlocked. If false, this achievement is visible to the user in the app's list of achievements prior to being unlocked.

    • Method Detail

      • getUnlockDate

        public void getUnlockDate(SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)
        Get the date that the user unlocked this achievement. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.

      • unlock

        public void unlock()
        Unlock the achievement and display a Swarm Notification to the user showing that this achievement was unlocked. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.

      • unlock

        public void unlock(SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)
        Unlock the achievement and display a Swarm Notification to the user showing that this achievement was unlocked. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.
        Parameters:
        cb - AchievementUnlockedCB callback returns true if this achievement was successfully unlocked and returns false otherwise. (null safe)

      • unlock

        public static void unlock(int achievementId)
        Unlock the achievement specified by the achievementId. The achievementId value can be found on the Swarm website in your Swarm Admin Panel. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.
        Parameters:
        achievementId - The identification number of the achievement you wish to unlock.

      • unlock

        public static void unlock(int achievementId,
          SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)
        Unlock the achievement specified by the achievementId. The achievementId value can be found on the Swarm website in your Swarm Admin Panel. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.
        Parameters:
        achievementId - The identification number of the achievement you wish to unlock.
        cb - AchievementUnlockedCB callback returns true if this achievement was successfully unlocked by this method call, and returns false otherwise. (null safe)

      • isUnlocked

        public void isUnlocked(SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)
        Check to see if this Achievement is unlocked. If the user is not logged in, this method is ignored.
        Parameters:
        cb - GotUnlockedCB callback returns true if this Achievement is unlocked, returns false otherwise.

      • isUnlocked

        public static void isUnlocked(int achievementId,
              SwarmAchievement.AchievementUnlockedCB cb)

        cb - GotUnlockedCB callback returns true if this Achievement is unlocked, returns false otherwise.
